reviews.review_text: quisper very crisp, nothing really standout but a great show worth having

Very good show This is a very good show, I did notice that there are parts that seem to skip like a record on this recording.  Other than that it's a nice solid show, I mean come on you have Dark Star, Comes a Time and Stella Blue all in one show.  

There is also a ton of banter going on with the band and the crowd, more than almost any show I've listened to.

             Jacob "Cob" Valverde

Fun Show Real fun show, great crowd banter.  Highlights for me were Greatest Story Ever Told and that lovely Dark Star > Comes a Time.  Interesting to hear them address the Pigpen situation, "He's at home, sick in bed."
